DISCLAIMER:

DB-OCR is a hardware-intensive AI system that includes vLLM with DeepSeek-OCR baked into a container. Running this software creates a local AI processing agent capable of analyzing images and PDFs. Users are responsible for ensuring that their system has sufficient GPU and memory resources to run this software safely. It is recommended to have a modern NVIDIA GPU, equivalent to or stronger than GeForce RTX 2070, with up-to-date drivers.

